---
import AppLayout from "../../layouts/AppLayout.astro";

const appName = "Fast Slow";
const primaryColor = "#F08549";
const secondaryColor = "#416FD3";
const backgroundColor = "#EFECE7";
---

<AppLayout title={`${appName} â€” Privacy Policy`} description={`${appName} Privacy Policy`}>
    <section class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6 py-16">
        <article class="prose max-w-none">
            <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold mb-4" style={`color: ${primaryColor}`}>Privacy Policy</h1>
            <p class="text-sm text-zinc-500 mb-8">Last updated: {new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-US', { year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric' })}</p>

            <p class="text-zinc-700 mb-8">
                Fast Slow is designed with privacy at its core. We believe your fasting journey is personal, 
                and your data should stay private. This policy explains how we protect your information and what 
                data we collect (spoiler: very little).
            </p>

            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-zinc-900 mb-4" style={`color: ${primaryColor}`}>What We Don't Collect</h2>
            <ul class="mb-8">
                <li>No personal information (name, email, phone)</li>
                <li>No location data or GPS tracking</li>
                <li>No browsing history or app usage across devices</li>
                <li>No account registration required</li>
                <li>No contact lists or social connections</li>
                <li>No health data beyond fasting times</li>
            </ul>

            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-zinc-900 mb-4" style={`color: ${primaryColor}`}>What We Store Locally</h2>
            <p class="text-zinc-700 mb-4">
                Fast Slow stores the following information locally on your device to provide core functionality. 
                This data never leaves your device unless you explicitly choose to back it up through your device's backup system.
            </p>
            <ol class="mb-8 list-decimal list-inside">
                <li><strong>Fasting Sessions:</strong> Start and end times of your fasting periods to track progress and show history</li>
                <li><strong>App Preferences:</strong> Your chosen fasting schedules, notification settings, and app theme preferences</li>
                <li><strong>Notification Permissions:</strong> Whether you've granted permission for fasting reminders and completion notifications</li>
            </ol>

            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-zinc-900 mb-4" style={`color: ${primaryColor}`}>App Store & Third-Party Services</h2>
            
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-900 mb-3">Apple App Store</h3>
            <p class="text-zinc-700 mb-4">
                Fast Slow is distributed through the Apple App Store. Apple may collect analytics data about app downloads, 
                usage statistics, and crash reports according to their privacy policy. This data is anonymized and 
                aggregated. You can opt out of sharing analytics with Apple in your device settings.
            </p>
            
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-900 mb-3">Fast Slow Plus Subscription</h3>
            <p class="text-zinc-700 mb-8">
                If you subscribe to Fast Slow Plus, your subscription is processed by Apple. We receive anonymized 
                transaction data to enable premium features but cannot identify individual users. All subscription 
                management is handled through your Apple ID.
            </p>

            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-zinc-900 mb-4" style={`color: ${primaryColor}`}>Data Security</h2>
            <p class="text-zinc-700 mb-4">
                Since your data stays on your device, you have complete control over its security. Your fasting data is 
                protected by your device's built-in security features, including:
            </p>
            <ul class="mb-8">
                <li>Device encryption and secure storage</li>
                <li>App sandbox isolation from other apps</li>
                <li>Your device passcode, Face ID, or Touch ID protection</li>
            </ul>

            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-zinc-900 mb-4" style={`color: ${primaryColor}`}>Children's Privacy</h2>
            <p class="text-zinc-700 mb-8">
                Fast Slow is not intended for children under 13 years of age. Intermittent fasting should only be practiced 
                by adults or with appropriate medical guidance. We do not knowingly collect any information from children 
                under 13. If you believe a child under 13 has used our app, please contact us immediately.
            </p>

            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-zinc-900 mb-4" style={`color: ${primaryColor}`}>Changes to This Policy</h2>
            <p class="text-zinc-700 mb-8">
                We may update this privacy policy from time to time to reflect changes in our practices or for legal reasons. 
                When we make changes, we will update the "Last updated" date at the top of this policy. For significant changes, 
                we may notify users through the app or other communication methods.
            </p>

            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-zinc-900 mb-4" style={`color: ${primaryColor}`}>Contact</h2>
            <p class="text-zinc-700">
                If you have any questions about this privacy policy or how Fast Slow handles your data, 
                please contact us via the <a href="/contact" class="underline" style={`color: ${primaryColor}`}>contact page</a>.
            </p>
        </article>
    </section>
</AppLayout>
